# GitHub Linguist configuration.
#
# The shipped product is the Rust TUI under rust/. The Python in this repo is
# dev tooling (dev/scripts), CI helpers, the operator console, and the optional
# Python fallback pipeline — support code, not the product. Keep it out of the
# language bar so the repository is classified as Rust.
*.py linguist-detectable=false

# Dev tooling and generated/report-heavy areas: exclude from stats entirely.
dev/** linguist-vendored
data_science/** linguist-vendored
